      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. those are good points. i noticed you mentioned the $100 billion cost for taxpayer services—my students are asking if that's a settled figure or if there's a lot of debate around how those costs are actually calculated. can you go into more detail on how proponents of stricter enforcement use those economic arguments to justify the policy? like, what's the core logic they use regarding national sovereignty and the social contract?",
